text: Vettor Pisani may refer to: *Vettor Pisani, a Venetian admiral *Italian submarine Vettor Pisani *Italian cruiser Vettor Pisani, armoured cruiser built for the Royal Italian Navy *Vettor Pisani (corvette), Italian naval corvette that left Italy in 1882 for a three-year scientific voyage round the world.
title: Vettor Pisani (disambiguation)
